title: (Minister for Tourism, Culture, Arts, Gaeltacht, Sport and Media) Order 2023.
heading: 1. This Order may be cited as the Appointment of Special Advisers
text_raw:
1. This Order may be cited as the Appointment of Special Advisers 
(Minister for Tourism, Culture, Arts, Gaeltacht, Sport and Media) Order 2023.

title: (Minister for Tourism, Culture, Arts, Gaeltacht, Sport and Media) Order 2023.
heading: 2. Tanya Warren, particulars of whose address have been deposited at the
text_raw:
2. Tanya Warren, particulars of whose address have been deposited at the 
offices of the Department of Tourism, Culture, Arts, Gaeltacht, Sport and 
Media, is appointed to be a Special Adviser to the Minister for Tourism, 
Culture, Arts, Gaeltacht, Sport and Media with effect from 17 December 2022.

title: (Minister for Tourism, Culture, Arts, Gaeltacht, Sport and Media) Order 2023.
heading: Juno McEnroe, particulars of whose address have been deposited at the
text_raw:
3. 

Juno McEnroe, particulars of whose address have been deposited at the 
offices of the Department of Tourism, Culture, Arts, Gaeltacht, Sport and 
Media, is appointed to be a Special Adviser to the Minister for Tourism, 
Culture, Arts, Gaeltacht, Sport and Media with effect from 17 December 2022. 

GIVEN under the Official Seal of the Government, 

14 February, 2023. 

LEO VARADKAR, 

Taoiseach 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 17th February, 2023.
